{"tid":316171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★無家者online game　玩家為街頭求生要乞討、翻垃圾、賣藝賺錢","createTime":"2017-07-10T13:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T14:23:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98d16e2e1810675c98940838f66f336f6cdfb979","tid":316171,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:56:52.000Z","msg":"發佈日期：2017-07-10 07:00<br />\n<br />\n在遊戲中你住在庇護中心，你只有5元，你的任務是找到一份工作、一個長期的住所。但找一份工作也並不容易，即使只是賣報紙的工，有時也會被拒絕。而且你要<span style=\"color: red;\">先以0.5元</span>購入報紙，再以1.5元賣出，而賣報紙和乞討一樣，成功的頻率一樣低&mdash;&mdash;問10個人大概只有1、2個會答應。<br />\n<br />\n每天8點前你都要回到庇護中心，取得床位與食物，但有時你顧着找食物、乞討，時間快到卻一直找不到庇護中心，於是你只能在街上睡，有時地板太冷，有時前一天下過雨，你就要與濕滑的地板入眠。開發商說，每天晚上都會發生不同的事，把你的人生推向不同的方向&mdash;&mdash;例如唯一陪伴你的狗走失了。<br />\n<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/687719/xlarge/ba57de38f11ebcae526aade3b9be145d.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F687719%2Fxlarge%2Fba57de38f11ebcae526aade3b9be145d.jpg&d=xrBEIkkbOI%2BdwT7Vu8BMYXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=7f66fa2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/687719/xlarge/ba57de38f11ebcae526aade3b9be145d.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社區/103071/無家者online-game-玩家為街頭求生要乞討-翻垃圾-賣藝賺錢-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%2F103071%2F%E7%84%A1%E5%AE%B6%E8%80%85online-game-%E7%8E%A9%E5%AE%B6%E7%82%BA%E8%A1%97%E9%A0%AD%E6%B1%82%E7%94%9F%E8%A6%81%E4%B9%9E%E8%A8%8E-%E7%BF%BB%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE-%E8%B3%A3%E8%97%9D%E8%B3%BA%E9%8C%A2-&d=xrBEIkkbOI%2BdwT7Vu8BMYXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c780524e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社區/103071/無家者online-game-玩家為街頭求生要乞討-翻垃圾-賣藝賺錢-</a>"},{"pid":"d8b295888004aa64ad6e2e6f8576e38cd9fd81d1","tid":316171,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T13:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/215722_f28a3075fde33c6510740a41c10a593f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F215722_f28a3075fde33c6510740a41c10a593f.jpg&h=bdf1ef26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"699e8f13450f419fc3afc14fc00f2b2df0e8d846","tid":316171,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"McDonalds"},{"pid":"3b46893fba3b40c5a0b818137071d59dbdf941ba","tid":316171,"uid":78900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:09:14.000Z","msg":"使乜訓街, 訓24小時M記有冷氣, 仲有水飲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲可以食人地食剩既薯條 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044c0f069ecb9804bd64088f5ff0c3008da7d68f","tid":316171,"uid":24660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T14:23:56.000Z","msg":"你今晚瞓邊，我嚟探你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}